items.name: Split Personality
explicitMods:
This Jewel's Socket has 25% increased effect per Allocated Passive Skill between
it and your Class' starting location
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: You need not go looking for a second opinion.

items.name: Watcher's Eye
explicitMods: Gain 8% of Maximum Mana as Extra Maximum Energy Shield while affected by Clarity
Unaffected by Chilled Ground while affected by Purity of Ice
items.descrText: Place into an allocated Jewel Socket on the Passive Skill Tree. Right click to remove from the Socket.
flavourText: One by one, they stood their ground against a creature
they had no hope of understanding, let alone defeating,
and one by one, they became a part of it.
